text: Sahiwal District () is a district in the Punjab province of Pakistan. The city of Sahiwal is the capital. Sahiwal is on GT Road. It is 167 km from Lahore. ==Tehsils== * Sahiwal Tehsil * Chichawatni Tehsil Category:Districts of British India Category:Sahiwal Division Category:Districts of Punjab (Pakistan)
title: Sahiwal District
